            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "For `maparg()`, consistency with the `:map` Ex command also needs to be considered, and `buffer_value` is not a buffer number but 0/1, so I don't think it makes sense to add `buf`.\r\n```suggestion\r\n  if (!compatible) {\r\n    PUT_C(dict, \"buf\", INTEGER_OBJ(buffer_value));\r\n  }\r\n```",
